        "id": 1166720
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-05-01T06:46:59Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Then, should we update the protocol first for supporting functions like SkipOnModel?\nIIUC currently given data in scope.* doesn\u0027t include model / platform information.",
